Package: macabout
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-tk, pciutils, dmidecode
Recommends: python3-pil, python3-pil.imagetk
Maintainer: PandaWood <pandawoude@gmail.com>
Description: About This Computer dialog, Apple-style
 A Linux desktop app that displays a styled "About This Mac"-inspired
 dialog showing distro, processor, memory, graphics, and serial number.
 Translates raw Linux hardware identifiers into clean marketing names.
